{"tid":2165637,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【入U？】男生偽造清華錄取通知書騙父母　遭踢爆後離家出走","createTime":"2020-08-20T03:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T04:42:30.000Z","uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"74acf61ab75ce950eaa3646d131d8348aca540f8","tid":2165637,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:11:56.000Z","msg":"<code>https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200820/mobile/bkn-20200820033056810-0820_00952_001.html</code><br />\n廣東湛江雷州市調風鎮東平村一名曹姓理科考生，早前偽造了「清華大學錄取通知書」欺騙父母；其父母不疑有詐，花了數萬元人民幣在村內大排筵席，東平村委會更掛起紅色橫幅，大放炮仗慶祝。惟及後有網民踢爆，曹男在高考中僅考獲235分，網傳曹父被當場氣昏。事件引起輿論熱議，有律師指出，雖然曹男或只為炫耀好玩，但已涉嫌偽造事業單位印章，觸犯法律。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65oo3Mo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65oo3Mo.jpg&h=20c41b1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，曹男自稱獲清華大學人工智能技術專業錄取，更拿着偽造的通知書四處與他人合照。惟有網民踢爆，曹在廣東省高考中僅考獲235分，本科排名346,310位，專科排名346,317位。事件其後愈揭愈多，有網民表示曹男早有前科，自稱考上重點中學的經歷也受到當地人質疑。另知情網民透露，曹的父母當初在村內大排筵席慶祝，惟父親得知真相後當場氣昏，送院搶救甦醒後，還大罵︰「呸，考得還沒我血壓高！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s2xpOdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs2xpOdf.jpg&h=004bfa62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n惟曹父周三（19日）接受內地傳媒時強調，自己沒被氣昏，血壓也沒升高，更沒有離開家鄉。他表示，自己依靠務農維生，離開家鄉根本生活不下去，但坦言心情「十分糟」。他又透露，兒子事後揚言「不再上學，要去打工」，且已離家出走，目前無法聯繫。他坦言，兒子「平時在家很聽話，都是他煮飯做菜」，沒想到竟會騙兒子。<br />\n另雷州市警方事後回應事件，稱該男生是為了向家人逞能，目前未涉及違法犯罪，會對其進行口頭教育。"},{"pid":"da68c54e4437e5061bf2af91676b0368c22e0808","tid":2165637,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"呸，考得還沒我血壓高！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de406d503db3b8c545f05c616534de142041c8b","tid":2165637,"uid":74334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"清華都有藥劑讀？"},{"pid":"209afdb84743bec42ac81b7dc0b204ab7043ec04","tid":2165637,"uid":161412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:15:04.000Z","msg":"之後曹父咪無飯開囉"},{"pid":"ac9a4ffc6acf2b3bd0df2adca7d6444a0d56db36","tid":2165637,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da68c54e4437e5061bf2af91676b0368c22e0808","tid":2165637,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"呸，考得還沒我血壓高！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef428f48944cc7713e7c3e3d6d519eeedd7356e4","tid":2165637,"uid":198278,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7de406d503db3b8c545f05c616534de142041c8b","tid":2165637,"uid":74334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"清華都有藥劑讀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"但佢證書上寫係人工智能技術"},{"pid":"a42312cafcbe0f94cce48dcb4a0e45dae00d50ff","tid":2165637,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef428f48944cc7713e7c3e3d6d519eeedd7356e4","tid":2165637,"uid":198278,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7de406d503db3b8c545f05c616534de142041c8b","tid":2165637,"uid":74334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"清華都有藥劑讀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"但佢證書上寫係人工智能技術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"明顯用潮文笑緊佢"},{"pid":"b8ec25ca1235310cd4db31ae0d33734494b762b9","tid":2165637,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"老豆幽默感幾好"},{"pid":"ff6d1b55adf9770e31cf1de1fc00edf64ebe9132","tid":2165637,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a42312cafcbe0f94cce48dcb4a0e45dae00d50ff","tid":2165637,"uid":3